==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Afflictive
<hw>Af*flic"tive</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>afflictif</ets>.]</ety> <def>Giving pain; causing continued or
repeated pain or grief; distressing.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Jove's
<xex>afflictive</xex> hand.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Pope.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Spreads slow disease, and darts <qex>afflictive</qex> pain.</q>
<rj><qau>Prior.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Afflictively</ent>⟦br⟧
